---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure | NaughtyCamSpot"
  description="Affiliate disclosure for NaughtyCamSpot growth services and launch routing."
>
  <section class="content-card space-y-4 text-sm text-white/70">
    <h1 class="section-heading">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p>
      NaughtyCamSpot uses affiliate routing for the guided launch lane. When you click a routed platform link and complete signup, we
      may earn a commission from that referral.
    </p>
    <ul class="space-y-3 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5 backdrop-blur-xl text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/55">
      <li>No employment or agency relationship.</li>
      <li>No guarantee of earnings.</li>
      <li>Accounts remain yours; you can leave anytime.</li>
      <li>Affiliate links support the guided launch lane.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      We provide growth guidance for active models and launch guidance for new models. We do not take over platform accounts, require
      passwords, or guarantee outcomes. All content on this site is educational or illustrative.
      If you have questions about this disclosure, contact <a class="text-rose-gold underline-offset-4 hover:underline" href="mailto:concierge@naughtycamspot.com">concierge@naughtycamspot.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
